title: Wooden Bracket, Pisa
medium: Graphite on off-white wove paper, folded, tipped into binding with fabric
description: Vertical sheet illustrating a single scroll bracket seen in profile and in elevation.  In profile the scroll is seen to rest against a small circular element that separates it from the surface behind.  The sheet has horizontal crease lines that create four sections. The verso has two very light sketches of flower and diamond tile pavement designs.
name: Album page
